name: Fly, baby, fly!
description:
Fly baby, fly! is an immersive VR experience where the user is invited to experience once again the journey every human takes right before they are born.

The user finds himself standing on a white cloud, held by a stork, ready to begin a fantastic trip.

  • Stork 3D model by: CadNav
  • Alien model by: Andrei Ilie
  • Using Unreal Engine Content
